#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31470"
msgid "Restore Madnox skin settings to day 1 out of the box startup values. Only affects skin settings, does not alter or change anything else like scripts or plugins."
msgstr "Restaura la configuración del skin de Madnox to day 1 out of the box startup values. Only affects skin settings, does not alter or change anything else like scripts or plugins."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31471"
msgid "Allows customization of default media flags without requiring outside hacks to the skin. This allows you to custom select which video container icons will be displayed for WebDL, 1080p, 720p etc. This can be reset at any time."
msgstr "Dexa la personalización de los indicadores multimedia por defectu ensin precisar cambeos esternos nel skin. Esto dexa escoyer qué iconos de contenedor de videu se van amosar para WebDL, 1080p, 720p, etc. Esto puede restablecese en cualquier momentu."

